description: Beaten out of a single thin sheet. It has 4 double perforations at equal distances round its rim with a small wire linked through each; in two cases a larger twisted ring hangs down from these like the handle of a cauldron. He added later, "Perhaps it should therefore be regarded as the scale of a measure."
